{"tid":1392520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"律政司檢控人員公開信，轟鄭若驊檢控決定，主要考慮政治因素","createTime":"2019-07-31T18:44:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T22:03:05.000Z","uid":201581,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b55d7e07ac0eb38447bed8bbafe7baa4e643ace7","tid":1392520,"uid":201581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:44:13.000Z","msg":"7.28上環衝突中逾 40 人被控暴動等罪名。一批自稱代表律政司部分檢控人員利用律政司的信紙，向全港市民發公開信，痛斥律政司司長鄭若驊其身不正，處理公眾活動案件時「主要考慮政治因素」，在沒有充份證據下堅持檢控，是「視檢控守則如糞土」。公開信又斥鄭若驊只向特首林鄭月娥叩頭，是愧當律政司司長。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士表示，今日至少有五位檢控官，包括高級檢控官同意發出該公開信。消息又批評，基本上鄭若驊一言堂、一面倒撐警，而因應近期反送中運動，鄭若驊及刑事檢控專員梁卓然現在每周都有與警方開會。<br />\n<br />\n該公開信的信頭為律政司刑事檢控科，並強調陳述「只代表部分檢控人員」，沒有署名，但以律政司信箋發出。公開信指出檢控最重要的兩項原則，是檢控前必須考慮是否有合理機會達致定罪，及檢控是否合乎公眾利益。公開信斥律政司司長鄭若驊及刑事檢控專員梁卓然「似乎忘記以上原則」。<br />\n<br />\n公開信批評鄭若驊「其身不正，又不是刑事法專才」，在處理牽涉大型公眾活動案件時，「主要考慮政治因素」，質疑她在沒有充份證據，沒有合理機會達致定罪，或不乎合公眾利益之下堅持檢控，是「視檢控守則如糞土」。公開信又斥梁卓然曾被法庭裁定為不誠實證人，又指他被鄭若驊踐踏，不能做好把關工作。<br />\n<br />\n這些檢控人員斥，鄭若驊及梁卓然在大是大非議題上，只會背誦範本對答以搪塞傳媒質詢，對內亦沒有安撫和穩定人心，「他們從來沒有真誠面向法律界和廣大香港市民。鄭只懂向特首叩頭，梁鄭他們都愧當刑事檢控專員和律政司司長這職銜」。<br />\n<br />\n公開信指721警黑勾結事件令所有人震驚和憤慨，香港法治面臨前所未有的衝擊，他們支持成立獨立委員會調查事件。他們認為需要一個有良心、有原則的人擔當律政司和刑事檢控專員。<br />\n<br />\n早前部分刑事檢控科律師向市民發公開信，指 7月21日元朗襲擊讓他們看到社會秩序崩潰，「部份執法者與暴徒狼狽為奸，我們無論如何中立都已經不能再保持沉默」，要求政府明確撤回修例，廣泛諮詢法律界和市民，並譴責任何一方使用暴力，又指理解廣大市民對政府充耳不聞感到憤怒，「我們都是香港人，我們都有參與遊行，我們同樣感到憤怒！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/律政司檢控人員公開信-轟鄭若驊檢控決定-主要考慮政治因素/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E4%BF%A1-%E8%BD%9F%E9%84%AD%E8%8B%A5%E9%A9%8A%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A-%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%2F&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGKCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=9e699e8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E4%BF%A1-%E8%BD%9F%E9%84%AD%E8%8B%A5%E9%A9%8A%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A-%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%2F&h=d724f25c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/律政司檢控人員公開信-轟鄭若驊檢控決定-主要考慮政治因素/</a>"},{"pid":"d7e954932fc410403ac749a704f5c7d4e4dcc479","tid":1392520,"uid":201581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:44:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"b3d81e90b96937b2901055c05827937ab4814d2b","tid":1392520,"uid":93350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5becb819e58c2e904654e83815aa101f2e95467","tid":1392520,"uid":201581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:44:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3e64c5221d3af7f30f04f98bd11534ce6c1afe","tid":1392520,"uid":191392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:45:44.000Z","msg":"想拎蚛蝈禁字list 大家請出招<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1392517\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1392517</a>"},{"pid":"b3f3af33c4d74e1cd97c984c52159c6d66ee39da","tid":1392520,"uid":201581,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:45:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好再呃自己 出面一切都係正常</span>"},{"pid":"6c1624d129047651e6c54d48f77d65484881633f","tid":1392520,"uid":201581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:46:10.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"f03157e645f32298d17e03669970fe4dac057785","tid":1392520,"uid":201581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:47:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9e0jkYJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9e0jkYJ.png&h=d7864048&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c6852e71c69c14fbc049aff2f6a9fce41edb5fc","tid":1392520,"uid":201581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:47:24.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da14ade8b0e077604b0d14a0abaa51ea61719855","tid":1392520,"uid":201581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:48:14.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"0ac26f09cfd219b323b3007f20259fa2a98e47d2","tid":1392520,"uid":201581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:48:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1bbb355fb3d81e6daca374b073d930533d81881","tid":1392520,"uid":201581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:49:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52f5733b4bb657edfab2a788e947ca48b705f1e4","tid":1392520,"uid":201581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:49:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db04c0489e604f16a757700d3275ef74419ad4c8","tid":1392520,"uid":201581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:50:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5cfb75a4476eb97ae7b2aae571d9d3d9e22e1b5","tid":1392520,"uid":201581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:50:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3817ff8180bc020459d0bc01a7d04e771b61d00","tid":1392520,"uid":201581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:51:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74520d2173246143a6c4f570ac951578d1ed3dd3","tid":1392520,"uid":201581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:52:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1afdf817aafd6706541a5750c1ec2c9ad174e448","tid":1392520,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:56:55.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErY1NGl2p_M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DErY1NGl2p_M&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGKCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=efb6b1eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErY1NGl2p_M</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwGX_Vgq-1G0&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGKCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=bf9b0120\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0</a><br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港！時代革命！<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong! <br />\nThe Revolution Of Our Times! </span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>五大訴求</strong></span></span></ins><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4. 追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>Hongkongers 5 Demands:</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n1. Full Withdrawal of the Extradition Bill<br />\n2. Retraction of the Characterisation of the Protestas a Riot<br />\n3. Release all Arrested Protesters<br />\n4. Accountability for Police and Yuen Long White Shirts Brutality<br />\n5. Implement Dual Universal Suffrage<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Rcba2Hh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcba2Hh.png&h=a61a5d44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/fm6yf2o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffm6yf2o.jpg&h=67e4b0d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時間無多，政府拖字訣，想我地自亂陣腳，行動規模必須升級</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b47c977c739d437cf87c20e3bf6a82fcd094cb","tid":1392520,"uid":267423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:09:36.000Z","msg":"香港已經係極權獨裁統治 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63da91ee58f8602693ab05698a83b5102e099539","tid":1392520,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:29:33.000Z","msg":"7.28上環衝突中逾 40 人被控暴動等罪名。一批自稱代表律政司部分檢控人員利用律政司的信紙，向全港市民發公開信，痛斥律政司司長鄭若驊其身不正，處理公眾活動案件時「主要考慮政治因素」，<span style=\"color: red;\">在沒有充份證據下堅持檢控，是「視檢控守則如糞土」</span>。公開信又斥鄭若驊只向特首林鄭月娥叩頭，是愧當律政司司長。<br />\n<br />\n即係無充份証據？<br />\n義士唔好灰心<br />\n可能好大機會打得甩<br />\n到時要告鳩鄭若嬅𨍭頭"},{"pid":"4ca73239ca6d9e0801721f5954034b5865a3b65d","tid":1392520,"uid":78695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/p6SPF3E.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fp6SPF3E.gif&h=6818fdd6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eae74651731c1e24be8c08308455be1e42191f85","tid":1392520,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:31:46.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"1c123702f4f743335dca512f2509536728fcd520","tid":1392520,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ca73239ca6d9e0801721f5954034b5865a3b65d","tid":1392520,"uid":78695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/p6SPF3E.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fp6SPF3E.gif&h=6818fdd6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:31:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416285392899e60b30cbea301f933187552a44e7","tid":1392520,"uid":201581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:49:52.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"2af2c19f62d29143f7292c0dc335d7ece0e47a56","tid":1392520,"uid":55168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T21:38:18.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"}]}